===Chieftains of the Dúnedain===
After the destruction of Arthedain by the attacks of Angmar the heirs of Isildur ceased to be kings.  Instead, they continued as chieftains of the remnant of the northern Dúnedain until Aragorn II was crowned as [[Aragorn|King Elessar]] of the [[Reunited Kingdom]].

